name: FushigiMixV1
description:
A Mix of CoolerWaifuDiffusion7030 and SD 2.1 base (512).

It can generate more ani-real images than the original CoolerWaifu, or WaifuDiffusion and Cool Japan Diffusion, which are the origins of CoolerWaifu.


My final goal on this series is to get something close to MoeSharpV1 only with NAI leak free SD 2.x based models, and from that point of view, it's still at the developing stage; further improvements may come in the future.

It does NOT contain NAI leak based models (nor is trained on NAI leak generated images), unlike most of the SD 1.x based anime/waifu models.
